text: Kamilla Sofie Vallin (born 18 August 1993) is a Danish professional racing cyclist. In 2013, she won the Danish National Road Race Championships and took the silver medal at the Danish National Time Trial Championships. She rides for Team Rytger. ==See also== * List of 2015 UCI Women's Teams and riders ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Danish female cyclists Category:People from Gentofte Municipality
